title: It’s Time For A Change
itunes:title: It’s Time For A Change
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’m a board-certified registered nurse and I was raised in public housing by my aunt because my mother had me when she was 16. After I graduated from high school, I found out my aunt was sleeping with my boyfriend so I beat her up and spent time in juvenile detention. From that point on, I was told that I wouldn’t amount to anything. I beat the odds and I got a nursing degree..............,.,.,.
